&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-hot-reload" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#hot-reload"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Hot reload&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We don't have a Hot Reload yet but it is on our roadmap. In the meantime, you can check branch &lt;a href="https://github.com/revery-ui/revery/tree/feat/hot-reload"&gt;feat/hot-reload&lt;/a&gt; to see the progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the meantime @mbernat has done a &lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/mbernat/abf651653c123374037c27377f41d0a0"&gt;script&lt;/a&gt; that allow to relaunch the APP when the binary changed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><author>revery-ui</author><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.com/revery-ui/revery</guid><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2020 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Schniz/fnm #2 in Reason, Today</title><link>https://github.com/Schniz/fnm</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;🚀 Fast and simple Node.js version manager, built in native ReasonML&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;h1 align="center"&gt;&lt;a id="user-content---fast-node-manager-fnm----" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#--fast-node-manager-fnm----"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
  Fast Node Manager (&lt;code&gt;fnm&lt;/code&gt;)
  &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/e0b149987887386e67c2a3f7524da88bcaafa35b/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f646f776e6c6f6164732f5363686e697a2f666e6d2f746f74616c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174"&gt;&lt;img alt="Amount of downloads" src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/e0b149987887386e67c2a3f7524da88bcaafa35b/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f646f776e6c6f6164732f5363686e697a2f666e6d2f746f74616c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174" data-canonical-src="https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/Schniz/fnm/total.svg?style=flat" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
